    },
    {
      "type": "accuracy",
      "location": "Introduction",
      "issue": "The opening uses dramatic phrasing ('Prices of memory are going crazy', 'The scariest thing is...').",
      "suggestion": "Do not flatten into academic prose. Use strong Chinese equivalents like '内存价格正陷入狂热' and '最令人胆寒的是...' to match the intensity."
    },
    {
      "type": "accuracy",
      "location": "Section: How the Cycle Will Evolve",
      "issue": "Long, dense sentences explaining the physical location of EUV adoption ('most in the congested region where access transistors... meet the memory storage capacitors').",
      "suggestion": "Break down into shorter clauses in Chinese: '主要集中在存取晶体管（用于读写存储单元）与存储电容（用于存储代表 0 或 1 的电荷）交汇的密集区域。'"
    },
